{"id":765,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":765,"title":"Isaiah 63","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 63"],[".studySummary",["i","The Second Coming will be a day of vengeance and also the year of the redeemed of the Lord—Then the Saints will praise the Lord and acknowledge Him as their father."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.1","order":"02.24.063.50234"},["b","1"],"Who",["i","is"],"this that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"cometh"],"from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Edom"],", with dyed garments from Bozrah? this",["i","that is"],"glorious in his apparel, travelling in the greatness of his strength? I that speak in righteousness, mighty to save."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.2","order":"02.24.063.50235"},["b","2"],"Wherefore",["i","art thou"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"red"],"in thine apparel, and thy garments like him that treadeth in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"winefat"],"?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.3","order":"02.24.063.50236"},["b","3"],"I have trodden the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"winepress"],"alone; and of the people",["i","there was"],"none with me: for I will tread them in mine anger, and trample them in my fury; and their blood shall be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"sprinkled"],"upon my garments, and I will stain all my raiment."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.4","order":"02.24.063.50237"},["b","4"],"For the day of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"vengeance"],["i","is"],"in mine heart, and the year of my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"redeemed"],"is come."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.5","order":"02.24.063.50238"},["b","5"],"And I looked, and",["i","there was"],"none to help; and I wondered that",["i","there was"],"none to uphold: therefore mine own arm brought",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"salvation"],"unto me; and my fury, it upheld me."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.6","order":"02.24.063.50239"},["b","6"],"And I will tread down the people in mine anger, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"make them drunk"],"in my fury, and I will bring down their strength to the earth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.7","order":"02.24.063.50240"},["b","7"],"¶I will mention the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"lovingkindnesses"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","and"],"the praises of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", according to all that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath bestowed on us, and the great",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"goodness"],"toward the house of Israel, which he hath bestowed on them according to his mercies, and according to the multitude of his lovingkindnesses."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.8","order":"02.24.063.50241"},["b","8"],"For he said, Surely they",["i","are"],"my people, children",["i","that"],"will not lie: so he was their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Saviour"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9","order":"02.24.063.50242"},["b","9"],"In all their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"affliction"],"he was afflicted, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"angel"],"of his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"presence"],"saved them: in his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"love"],"and in his pity he",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"redeemed"],"them; and he bare them, and",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_9f"},"carried"],"them all the days of old."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10","order":"02.24.063.50243"},["b","10"],"¶But they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"rebelled"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"vexed"],"his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"holy Spirit"],": therefore he was turned to be their",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"enemy"],",",["i","and"],"he fought against them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11","order":"02.24.063.50244"},["b","11"],"Then",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"he remembered"],"the days of old, Moses,",["i","and"],"his people,",["i","saying,"],"Where",["i","is"],"he that brought them up out of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sea"],"with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"shepherd"],"of his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"flock"],"? where",["i","is"],"he that put his holy Spirit within",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_11e"},"him"],"?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.12","order":"02.24.063.50245"},["b","12"],"That led",["i","them"],"by the right hand of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Moses"],"with his glorious arm,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"dividing"],"the water before them, to make himself an everlasting name?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.13","order":"02.24.063.50246"},["b","13"],"That led them through the deep, as an horse in the wilderness,",["i","that"],"they should not stumble?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14","order":"02.24.063.50247"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"As a beast goeth"],"down into the valley, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Spirit"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"caused",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"him"],"to rest: so didst thou lead thy people, to make thyself a glorious",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"name"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.15","order":"02.24.063.50248"},["b","15"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Look"],"down from heaven, and behold from the habitation of thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"holiness"],"and of thy glory: where",["i","is"],"thy zeal and thy strength,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"the"],"sounding of thy bowels and of thy mercies toward me? are they restrained?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.16","order":"02.24.063.50249"},["b","16"],"Doubtless thou",["i","art"],"our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"father"],", though Abraham",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"be ignorant"],"of us, and Israel acknowledge us not: thou, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","art"],"our father, our redeemer; thy name",["i","is"],"from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"everlasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.17","order":"02.24.063.50250"},["b","17"],"¶O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", why hast thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"made"],"us to err from thy ways,",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"hardened"],"our heart from thy fear? Return for thy servants’ sake, the tribes of thine inheritance."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.18","order":"02.24.063.50251"},["b","18"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"people"],"of thy holiness have possessed",["i","it"],"but a little while: our adversaries have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"trodden"],"down thy sanctuary."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.19","order":"02.24.063.50252"},["b","19"],"We are",["i","thine:"],"thou never barest rule over them; they were not called by thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"name"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.1a","order":"02.24.063.50253"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.1b","order":"02.24.063.50255"},["b","1b"],["span.small","IE"],"the worldly nations;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.36"},"D&C 1:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.2a","order":"02.24.063.50257"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/49.11.11-12"},"Gen. 49:11 (11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.13.13-15"},"Rev. 19:13 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.107"},"D&C 76:107"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.48.46-50"},"133:48 (46–50)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.2b","order":"02.24.063.50259"},["b","2b"],["span.small","HEB"],"press; i.e., the winepress and the vat for collecting the juice of the grapes."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.3a","order":"02.24.063.50261"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.19.17-20"},"Rev. 14:19 (17–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.15"},"19:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.106"},"D&C 88:106"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.3b","order":"02.24.063.50263"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/8.30"},"Lev. 8:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.51"},"D&C 133:51"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.4a","order":"02.24.063.50265"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vengeance"},"TG Vengeance"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.4b","order":"02.24.063.50267"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.20"},"Zeph. 3:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.52"},"D&C 133:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.5a","order":"02.24.063.50269"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/59.16"},"Isa. 59:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.6a","order":"02.24.063.50271"},["b","6a"],["span.small","OR"],"break them in pieces (according to several Hebrew texts)."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.7a","order":"02.24.063.50273"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kindness"},"TG Kindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.7b","order":"02.24.063.50275"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.52"},"D&C 133:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.8a","order":"02.24.063.50277"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9a","order":"02.24.063.50279"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.53"},"D&C 133:53"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/affliction"},"TG Affliction"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"Compassion"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9b","order":"02.24.063.50281"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.20.20-23"},"Ex. 23:20 (20–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9c","order":"02.24.063.50283"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/33.14"},"Ex. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9d","order":"02.24.063.50285"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/love"},"Love"],"."],["div",{"id":"9e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9e","order":"02.24.063.50287"},["b","9e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.3.2-4"},"D&C 138:3 (2–4)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"},"TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"},"Jesus Christ, Redeemer"],"."],["div",{"id":"9f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.9f","order":"02.24.063.50289"},["b","9f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/46.4.3-4"},"Isa. 46:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10a","order":"02.24.063.50291"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/14.11.11-12"},"Num. 14:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10b","order":"02.24.063.50293"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Loss of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10c","order":"02.24.063.50295"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.10d","order":"02.24.063.50297"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.4.4-5"},"Lam. 2:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11a","order":"02.24.063.50299"},["b","11a"],["span.small","IE"],"His people remembered."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11b","order":"02.24.063.50301"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-deliverance-of"},"TG Israel, Deliverance of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11c","order":"02.24.063.50303"},["b","11c"],["span.small","OR"],"shepherds."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11d","order":"02.24.063.50305"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church"},"TG Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"11e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.11e","order":"02.24.063.50307"},["b","11e"],["span.small","OR"],"them."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.12a","order":"02.24.063.50309"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/77.20"},"Ps. 77:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.12b","order":"02.24.063.50311"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.21"},"Ex. 14:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.13"},"Ps. 78:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14a","order":"02.24.063.50313"},["b","14a"],["span.small","OR"],"As cattle go."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14b","order":"02.24.063.50315"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-spirit-of"},"TG God, Spirit of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14c","order":"02.24.063.50317"},["b","14c"],["span.small","OR"],"them."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.14d","order":"02.24.063.50319"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/9.16"},"Ex. 9:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/106.8"},"Ps. 106:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.9"},"Ezek. 20:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.15a","order":"02.24.063.50321"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/26.15"},"Deut. 26:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/33.14"},"Ps. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.15b","order":"02.24.063.50323"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.15c","order":"02.24.063.50325"},["b","15c"],["span.small","IE"],"the abundance of Thy tenderness."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.16a","order":"02.24.063.50327"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.6"},"Deut. 32:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/29.10"},"1 Chr. 29:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/64.8"},"Isa. 64:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.16b","order":"02.24.063.50329"},["b","16b"],["span.small","IE"],"Such forefathers as Abraham and Jacob, long dead, were not available to help."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.16c","order":"02.24.063.50331"},["b","16c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-eternal-nature-of"},"TG God, Eternal Nature of"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.17a","order":"02.24.063.50333"},["b","17a"],["span.small","JST"],"Isa. 63:17 …",["i","suffered"],"us to err from thy ways, and",["i","to harden"],"our heart …"],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.17b","order":"02.24.063.50335"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hardheartedness"},"TG Hardheartedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.18a","order":"02.24.063.50337"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/7.6"},"Deut. 7:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.18b","order":"02.24.063.50339"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scr